
Sometimes,there are choices,one may lead you right,the other left,one may be correct,the other incorrect,Sometimes,choices are all that we,have.These choices judge,who we are,who we will become,and what we shall deserve.Sometimes,choices are the best decision,or the worst.Choices can breathe,Choices can hurt,Choices can live,Choices can burn.Every moment,a choice is made,a choice is complete,a choice is regretted.Sometimes,we live on our choices,and sometimes,we die,knowing we failed it.But,some choices,live a lifetime,the right choice.Positive,Negative,Right,Wrong,Left,Right,Straight,Choices.